Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:53.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:03:00.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:03.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:06.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate \Nalliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But caught up in the current \Nking Doflamingo's agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were trapped in the Birdcage \Nalong with the entire island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with the Straw Hats fighting\Nthe Donquixote Family fiercely,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Law finally clash with Doflamingo\Nat the Royal Palace!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside my body now,\Nstrings are repairing my inner organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How smartly you can use your ability is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The Color of the Supreme King, colliding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He uses it, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mingo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doffy's madness will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...destroy everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Eagle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Athlete!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:05:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Unassailable!\NThe Stunning Secret of Trebol!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick-Stickem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't think a weakling like you can beat Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Let go of me! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait here struggling!\NWe'll kill you in turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, we'll start with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Doffy, I'll stall Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush Law's head while you have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't do it, Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me! Tra-guy can't move even one millimeter now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "In turn"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! This jerk is so icky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or not! Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could hit a Logia eater with the Color of Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now, do you think my power is the Logia type?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, that crap doesn't work against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rubber idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:07:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right - it's no use.\NHe's a papier-mâché bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Papier-mâché?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than anything,\NI didn't want to sit on the Heart throne
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I didn't want to be grouped together with idiots like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call us top executives idiots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you still can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying, you half-dead moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We top executives {\i1}are{\i0}\Nthe foundation of the Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive anyone for making fun of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick-Stickem...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Tra-guy can't even move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta teach this brat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy will always be the absolute king!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there is no gap between him\Nand us current top executives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one day 30-something years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we four picked up this immense gift\Nthat fell from heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gave him power and brought him up\Nto be a charismatic force for evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone got knocked out?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That must be "Haki"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Haki of the Color of the Supreme King!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:09:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the man who was chosen by heaven!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you want me to give you...\Nthe strength to take revenge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the Holyland\Nby taking your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost got killed\Nin the Holyland of Mariejois?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even bringing them your father's head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad that you came back alive!\NIt's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy, you have the quality of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We swear to support you in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:10:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy, in return, let us have a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Doffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's the matter, Doffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some hoodlum did this. I wish he'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, is it you who hurt Doffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that brat!\NI just teased him a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just hurt that kid a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow!\NWhat's wrong with you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Donquixote Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... You got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He passed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with this brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy likes your turf.\NWe need you guys to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adios!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!\NDid somebody hurt you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just fell because the road was uneven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An uneven road?! Which town was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. This needs to be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:13:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Doflamingo Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, Doffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:21.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one must be allowed to rebel against you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the man who will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...become the king of the sea someday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We set up Doffy as a king\Nand showed our dignity to our subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Doffy and we four have been thinking of\Nthe Family equally and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,brought it to its present level!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a true family!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand, Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember that\Nmy mucus is flammable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can shut your annoying mouth up instantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A true family?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equally?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only you guys who are thinking\Nlike that, Trebol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His own ambition is everything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't give a damn about you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, even you, who acts like you're the chief of staff, only look like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Doflamingo's foolish puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-F-Foolish puppet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't fall for it, Trebol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're inside the Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brat was barely alive already but I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,restrained his movement with my mucus in addition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can he do in these circumstances?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna blow it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shut your smart-ass mouth\Nin the cruelest way I can think of!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, open your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shove this into your throat\Nand impale you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna blow it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shut your smart-ass mouth\Nin the cruelest way I can think of!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, open your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shove this into your throat\Nand impale you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a captain of a ship, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave both you and Doflamingo\Nin Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}'s hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lose my prestige!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even move! What can you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The arm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sterben Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:14.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE SMILE FACTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, you guys?\NYou turned to the town all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know why but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it feels like a huge load has been\Nlifted off my chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We don't have time for that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finished destroying the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's run from the approaching Birdcage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hurry or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood! He got slashed and bled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A slim guy came out of the mucus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why my punch got through his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you used...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your disembodied arm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:20:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You die with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He's gonna set fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you along!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Palace burst into flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Viola! What's going on at the Royal Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the executives, Trebol got defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Luffy okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Great! He's alive!\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes Doflamingo the only one remaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffyland!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he all right?\NWe got to back him up somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not do anything.\NYou might give him trouble to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Even Trafalgar Law who has\Nthe same title of Warlord as Doflamingo, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…in quite bad shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawland!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Hand me Tra-guy-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! That'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him! Tra-guy cornered Mingo enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! His arm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs! Spider Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawland's arm is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could they do this?!\NTra-guy-{\i1}kun{\i0}, stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything unnecessary!\NHe's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't been dismissed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.78,0:22:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk! He's still going for Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a finisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullet String!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hawk Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:22:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robiland!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Carrying on Law's ambition and with everybody's hopes\Non his shoulders, Luffy fights!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:17.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doflamingo's powerful techniques squarely target him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:19.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Hawk blasts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.55,0:23:22.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While time is ticking away until all people\Nin Dressrosa get wiped out,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:26.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the all-out decisive battle\Nbetween the two now begins!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Anger Erupts! I Will Take Everything upon Myself!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
